    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have caramelised, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until thickened to a pasta sauce consistency – this is your <strong>vegetable sauce</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>basil stalks</strong> (save the leaves for garnish!) and add them to the pan</p>",
