    {
      "instruction": "<p>Layer some of the <strong>vegetable sauce</strong> over the bottom of an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, then top with<strong> half </strong>of your<strong> lasagne sheets</strong></p><p>Repeat this process until you end up with a final layer of<strong> </strong>lasagne sheets</p><p>Tip: You may need to layer differently depending on the size of your dish!</p>",
