    {
      "instruction": "<p>Finally top with the <strong>cheese sauce</strong>,<strong> </strong>making sure all of the lasagne is covered</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> directly over the cheese sauce<strong> </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 30-35 min or until the lasagne<strong> </strong>is cooked – this is your <strong>Mediterranean-style vegetable lasagne</strong></p>",
