      "instruction": "<p>Allow the <strong>Mediterranean-style vegetable lasagne</strong> to cool slightly before serving (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Tear the<strong> basil leaves</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>Mediterranean-style vegetable lasagne</strong> and garnish with the <strong>torn basil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
